      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Your thick fur protects you from certain environmental hazards and makes you resistant to some types of @Compendium[sfrpg.rules.aKqRtg165rAly1Cc]{Poisons}.<br><strong>Prerequisites</strong>: Skittermander or ysoki.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelName\"><strong>Benefit</strong>: You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to Fortitude saves against cold and heat dangers. In addition, you gain a +4 circumstance bonus to Fortitude saves made to avoid contracting contact @Compendium[sfrpg.rules.GnEF27Oot3zqTaBQ]{Diseases} and @Compendium[sfrpg.rules.aKqRtg165rAly1Cc]{Poisons}.<br></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelName\"><strong>Special</strong>: At the GMâ€™s discretion, other furred races might meet the prerequisites for this feat.</span></p>"
